reviewText: Our granddaughter loves everything that's Minnie Mouse.  She especially likes the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse videos.  Her favorite is Minnie-rella which we have all watched close to 50 times.  My only complaint about this DVD is that the cartoons are not full-screen like the Minnie-rella DVD.  But 3-year-olds don't pay any attention to that :-)  Good clean and educational stories for toddlers.
